an class=\"avia-single-number __av-single-number\" data-number_format=\"\" data-number=\"000\" data-start_from=\"0\">000<\/span><span class=\"avia-no-number\">+ S.F.<\/span><\/strong><div class='avia-animated-number-content' ><p>Across all Facilities<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- close content main div --><\/div><\/div><\/div><div id='after_section_4'  class='main_color av_default_container_wrap container_wrap sidebar_right' style=' '  ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-small alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-63'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'><div class=\"flex_column av_one_full  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-15  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_button_big  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  \" ><section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><p>Since its founding, PPS has fostered a core mantra of \u201cwe care, we solve, and we own it\u201d that has empowered its team to deliver a comprehensive array of products and services. Our success is based on our team\u2019s innovation, critical thinking and most importantly, their type of practical problem-solving that our customers appreciate.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Power Plant Services offers unmatched experience as an aftermarket service provider with: <\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Over 500 years combined experience in parts manufacturing<\/li>\n<li>Over 250 years combined experience in performing field and shop repairs<\/li>\n<li>Over 100 years of combined experience in power plant engineering<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>In addition to our industry reputation and proven track record, PPS is proud of having impressive credentials to support our value proposition as a premier power plant services\u2019 provider, which include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>AS9100:<\/li>\n<li>ISO9001<\/li>\n<li>R Stamp<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Power Plant Services\u00a0is also known for its commitment to the development and application of internal best practices that extend beyond the quality assurance of our certifications and standards.<\/p>\n<p><strong>If you are ready to start a conversation to explore how Power Plant Services can meet your needs, contact us at 708-345-8600 to engage one of our knowledgeable techs or service representatives.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><\/p>\n<div  class='avia-button-wrap avia-button-center  avia-builder-el-17  el_after_av_one_full  avia-builder-el-last ' ><a href='https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/contact\/' class='avia-button avia-button-fullwidth  avia-font-color-theme-color av-icon-on-hover avia-icon_select-yes-right-icon avia-color-custom '  style='background-color:#0f3e96; ' ><span class='avia_iconbox_title' >REQUEST A QUOTE<\/span><span class='avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_right' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='\ue83c' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'><\/span><div class='av-button-description av-button-description-below'><p>Power Plant Services is always ready to meet the need of our customers, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days of the year.<\/p>\n<\/div><span class='avia_button_background avia-button avia-button-fullwidth avia-color-custom' style='background-color:#d10202;'><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/63"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ppsvcs.c